name: DIRECTIONALS THAT MOVE US
description: In the midst of the chaos of the big city, we are often moved in opposite directions from our dreams and ideals. It's almost impossible to see our goals along the way. It's a constant challenge. The world has never been the same again, and the bottom line is that we are all the same, going in different directions and with different goals. But which is the right path to take, that of reason or emotion? - 3205x4807 px - 300 ppi
